    {
      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Soak the <strong>skewers</strong> in water (this prevents them from burning whilst cooking)</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add 3/4 of the<strong> sliced onion</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1657003581919-x200.jpg",
