            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining ground almonds </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>softened butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>almond butter mix</strong></p><p>Spread the <strong>almond butter mix </strong>equally over the <strong>garlic & coriander naans</strong>, then transfer them to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 7-8 min or until golden – these are your <strong>almond naans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
