            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>chicken pasanda</strong> over the <strong>basmati rice </strong>with the <strong>almond naans </strong>to the side</p><p>Serve the <strong>paneer & pepper skewers </strong>to the side and garnish with the <strong>pink quick-pickled onion</strong> and <strong>herb chutney</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
